OL,3,CLong-awaited nama trial gets underway
OL,5,FThe rules of a Stormont committee were
OL,6,Fsubverted in 2015 to cause "political
OL,7,Fembarrassment" to former first
OL,8,Fminister Peter Robinson, a court has
OL,9,Fbeen told.
OL,11,FThe trial of loyalist activist Jamie
OL,12,FBryson, former Sinn Fein MLA Daithi
OL,13,FMcKay and Thomas O'Hara on charges
OL,14,Frelated to a committee hearing that
OL,15,Fexamined the sale of the National
OL,16,FAsset Management Agency's (Nama)
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland assets got under way
OL,18,Fon Tuesday.
