OL,5,FDUP chairman Lord Morrow was among the
OL,6,Fwitnesses who gave evidence on the
OL,7,Ffirst day of the trial at Belfast
OL,8,FCrown Court.
OL,10,FMcKay, 43, of Loughan Road,
OL,11,FDunnamanagh denies committing
OL,12,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,14,FBryson, 35, from Rosepark, Donaghadee,
OL,15,Fand O'Hara, 40, from Lisnahunshin
OL,16,FRoad, Cullybackey, both deny
OL,17,Fconspiring to commit misconduct in
