OL,5,FThe charges relate to Bryson's 2015
OL,6,Fappearance before the Stormont
OL,7,Fcommittee, chaired by McKay, which was
OL,8,Finvestigating the sale of the Nama's
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland assets to a US
OL,10,Finvestment fund.
OL,12,FA criminal probe was launched after
OL,13,Fthe publication of leaked Twitter
OL,14,Fmessages between Bryson, McKay and the
OL,15,Faccount of O'Hara, who at the time was
OL,16,Fa Sinn Fein activist in north Antrim.
OL,18,FMcKay quit as an MLA within hours of
OL,19,Fthe Twitter messages being published
OL,20,Fin August 2016.
