OL,5,FThe Stormont Finance Committee inquiry
OL,6,Fwas set up in 2015 amid political
OL,7,Fcontroversy over the multimillion-
OL,8,Fpound sale of Nama's property
OL,9,Fportfolio north of the border.
OL,11,FNama, the so-called bad bank created
OL,12,Fby the Irish government to deal with
OL,13,Fthe toxic loans of bailed-out lenders
OL,14,Fduring the economic crash, sold its
OL,15,F800 Northern Ireland-linked properties
OL,16,Fto investment fund Cerberus for #1.2
OL,17,Fbillion.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
