OL,5,FGiving evidence to the committee in
OL,6,F2015, Bryson used Assembly privilege
OL,7,Fto name former DUP leader Mr Robinson
OL,8,Fas a beneficiary of the sale.
OL,10,FThe then-first minister of Northern
OL,11,FIreland strongly rejected any
OL,12,Fsuggestion he benefited from the deal.
OL,13,FAll other parties involved in the
OL,14,Ftransaction also denied wrongdoing.
OL,16,FOpening the case on Tuesday,
OL,17,Fprosecuting barrister Toby Hedworth KC
OL,18,Fsaid it concerned a "successful
OL,19,Fattempt to subvert the rules of
OL,20,Fprocedure of a Stormont committee".
