OL,5,FHe said the purpose of this had been
OL,6,Fto cause "considerable political
OL,7,Fembarrassment" to Mr Robinson and
OL,8,Fothers.
OL,10,FHe said: "Those very rules of
OL,11,Fprocedure had been decided by the
OL,12,Fcommittee to protect a very
OL,13,Fsubstantial police enquiry into just
OL,14,Fthe sort of corruption that these
OL,15,Fdefendants were seeking to allege.
OL,17,F"That is why, say the prosecution,
OL,18,Fthis went way beyond what can be
OL,19,Fdeemed acceptable and had the
OL,20,Fpotential to place that police inquiry
OL,21,Fat risk."
