OL,5,FThe barrister said the finance
OL,6,Fcommittee had taken a public vote on
OL,7,Fhow the loyalist activist's evidence
OL,8,Fwould be heard, but were "unaware that
OL,9,FMcKay and Bryson, assisted by Mr
OL,10,FO'Hara, were secretly working together
OL,11,Fto subvert those very rules".
OL,13,FMr Hedworth said they had engaged in
OL,14,F"deliberate subterfuge".
