OL,5,F"Mr McKay had contrived how evidence
OL,6,Fwould be given in public session when
OL,7,Fit should have been given in private
OL,8,Fsession, and allowed it to happen when
OL,9,Fhe had the knowledge of what was to be
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Via his agreement with Mr Bryson,
OL,13,Fthere was a conspiracy to allow that
OL,14,Fto happen with Mr O'Hara being a vital
OL,15,Fand knowing cog in the wheel."
OL,17,FThe first witness in the trial was the
OL,18,FSammy Morrison, who at the time was
OL,19,Fthe PA to TUV leader Jim Allister.
