OL,5,FHe told the court that in August 2016,
OL,6,Fhe had received a phone call from
OL,7,FBryson telling him he would forward
OL,8,Femails containing Twitter messages
OL,9,Fbetween the loyalist activist and
OL,10,FMcKay which were going to be the basis
OL,11,Fof a story on the Nolan Show the
OL,12,Ffollowing day.
OL,14,FMr Morrison said the messages were
OL,15,Fthen sent to him by Bryson via emails
OL,16,Fand after reading some of them, he
OL,17,Fforwarded the messages to Mr Allister.
OL,19,FThe witness said he had subsequently
OL,20,Fgiven permission for a PSNI officer to
OL,21,Fretrieve the emails from his computer.
