OL,6,Fthat Peter Robinson was going to be
OL,7,Fnamed by Bryson during his committee
OL,8,Fappearance.
OL,10,FMr Morrison said: "I think everybody
OL,11,Fknew that when Jamie was coming to
OL,12,Fgive evidence before the committee
